Introduction

Jang Hyunseung, formerly known by the stage name Able, is a South Korean singer currently signed to MPLIFY Records. He is best known as a former member of the boy group B2ST and the co-ed subunit Trouble Maker. Jang made his solo debut on May 8, 2015, with the extended play My. After parting ways with Cube Entertainment in 2021, he briefly promoted under Mine Field before signing with MPLIFY Records in 2025, as announced through the label’s official social media channels.
